data.description: Welcome home to this like-new traditional style 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath open concept home! Large kitchen with white cabinets, stone countertops, stainless steel appliances, open to family room with fireplace. Separate dining room. Private deck overlooking backyard! Spacious Master with en-suite bathroom featuring dual vanity and separate tub/shower. Two additional bedrooms with plenty of space and laundry room on 2nd level. Full, unfinished terrace level that is already stubbed for a bath! Possible assumable FHA loan under 5%.
